name: Dinari EEM
description: The Dinari EEM dShares token (EEM.d) represents 1:1 ownership of shares in the iShares MSCI Emerging Markets ETF (NYSE Arca: EEM), an exchange-traded fund designed to track the investment results of an index composed of large- and mid-cap stocks from emerging market economies. Each EEM.d token is fully backed by a corresponding EEM ETF share, securely held in a transparent and auditable treasury. By leveraging blockchain technology, EEM.d provides investors with exposure to diversified equity investments across emerging markets, while benefiting from 24/7 trading, fractional ownership, instant settlement, and enhanced liquidity.
